# Mini Frontend Project

# Project Overview
This project is a mini frontend website created as part of Week 3 task.  
It includes multiple interconnected pages styled with a common CSS file.

# Pages Included
- Home Page (index.html)
- Registration Page (register.html)
- Login Page (login.html)
- Contact Page (contact.html)

# Folder Structure
Week3_Frontend_Project/
- index.html
- register.html
- login.html
- contact.html
- style.css
- script.js
- README.md

# Features
- Navigation bar linking all pages
- Registration form
- Login form
- Contact form
- Modern gradient background
- Reusable CSS styling
- Clean and organized layout

# Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Basic JavaScript

# How to Run
1. Open the folder Week3_Frontend_Project.
2. Open index.html in any web browser.
3. Use navigation links to move between pages.

# Learning Outcomes
- Multi-page website creation
- Folder structure organization
- Navigation linking
- Form design
- Styling using external CSS

# Author
Created as part of Week 3 Frontend Development task.